/
proc : demonstrates file system that makes access to kernel of info.
etc : setting files, configuration files and etc
boot : files updated, downloaded are here
home : is the location of users, here everything is personal, 2 people have
       different codes 

UNIX operators
>> redirect the output of a command onto the end of an existing file
<  redirect a file as input to a program
;  command separator
&  execute a command in a background and immediately get your shell back
&& command separator (runs the 2nd command if the 1st finishes without errors)

Trapping: Handling Signals
trap "echo dont hangup" 1 2 

Debugging
set -xv (turn on); v option prints each line as it is read
		   x option displays the command and its arguements
		   n checks for syntax errors
